[[Translation:en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Smooth economy]]
This [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Advanced Settings/Economy#enable-smooth-economy-more-smaller-changes|Advanced Settings]] "evens out" the fluctuations in the economy.  

== Description ==

Normally, the economy only changes in large jumps (of 50%) at irregular intervals.  When this patch is enabled, there will be smaller changes at more frequent intervals.


